blocked. The phone's call history
has been erased.

168
00:12:22,119 --> 00:12:24,239
God, they move fast.

169
00:12:24,239 --> 00:12:27,680
You ask me, these guys are
using Weevils to carry
out the perfect murder.

170
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:31,560
No fingerprints, no traces
of recognisable DNA,...

171
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:34,000
