172
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,480
Nothing to connect anyone
to the murder.

173
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:39,160
Right. Should be a piece
of piss to find the killer, then.

174
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:43,600
What about this guy?
Someone's got to break it
to his wife that he's dead.

175
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:06,880
